  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Sergeant Darya Nevic of the Cadian 217th is a sniper on the frozen manufactorum world Attruso, where the T'au invasion has made every kill into propaganda. She is not Cadian-born, and the regiment's true sons never let her forget it, yet Imperial officers want her turned into a symbol while the T'au promise a cleaner loyalty across the lines. As winter and casualties close in, Darya has to decide whether she can become the legend her soldiers need without surrendering the person beneath it. A line-soldier war story about identity, morale, and useful lies.",
